            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deae Fortunae <lb n="2"/>sanctae balineu<supplied reason="lost">m</supplied> <lb n="3"/>vetustate conlap<lb break="no" n="4"/>sum <expan><abbr>expl</abbr><ex>oratores</ex></expan> Stu<supplied reason="lost">ri</supplied> <lb n="5"/>et <expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>tones</ex></expan> gentiles <supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> <lb n="6"/>officiales <abbr>Brit</abbr><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>deditic</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">Alexan</del><lb break="no" n="8"/><del rend="erasure">drianorum</del> de <lb n="9"/>suo <expan><abbr>restituer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> cu<lb break="no" n="10"/><expan><abbr>ra</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> agente <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Ro<lb break="no" n="11"/>mano |(centurione) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XXII <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>rimigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> Lupo et Maximo </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die letzte Zeile befindet sich auf dem Sockelprofil. (B): CIL 13, 06592; Lemosse; AE 1983; AE 1897; ILS; RSO; Conrady; Schmidt Heidenreich: geringfügig abweichende Textwiedergaben.</p>
